  "summary": [
    "Add CRM destination profiles backed by synchronized WhatsApp contacts and groups",
    "Add deterministic, human-reviewable routing rules with priorities, fallbacks, conflicts and manual overrides",
    "Create traceable CRM dispatch batches from finalized official-letter complete PDFs",
    "Generalize immutable WhatsApp previews to support CRM sources without changing the AntiDengue planner contract",
    "Freeze exact recipients, messages, complete PDFs and checksums before explicit approval",
    "Reuse the existing WhatsApp approval, task outbox, NATS, gateway delivery, retry and audit infrastructure",
    "Block duplicate sends, unavailable destinations, changed packets, oversized packets and unsafe confidential routes",
    "Add dispatch dashboard, routing workspace, explainable route testing, batch review and delivery history",
    "Run complete tests and Astro build by default with database-first automatic rollback"
  ],
